{"type":"message","id":"9556ebe4","parentId":"2716d7da","timestamp":"2026-04-10T10:31:05.803Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check what channels are configured. The cron is called \"afternoon-jokes\" - this seems like it should post to a group. I should find the right channel/chat to post to.\n\nLet me check the cron job to see what channel it's supposed to post to.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ccv2dzga0ha_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":203,"output":157,"cacheRead":28992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29352,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775817060879,"responseId":"gen-1775817061-XN6KvZw9XRuxDeSAIT3K"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc7efa99","parentId":"9556ebe4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T10:31:05.841Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7ccv2dzga0ha_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"8c22f5b7-2a79-4790-b9dd-6cab24e79588\",\n      \"name\": \"afternoon-jokes\",\n      \"description\": \"Daily afternoon jokes at 4pm IST\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774753813927,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775730644576,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 16 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Kolkata\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 0\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"1. Search web for actually funny dark one liners, stupid dad jokes, good simple jokes that land. No boring generic ones.\\n2. Pick exactly 2.\\n3. Start with: \\\"Found these jokes today 😏\\\"\\n4. Post first joke, then add one tiny natural reaction comment + emoji like a real person would\\n5. Post second joke, same: small honest reaction comment + emoji\\n6. No extra fluff, no explanations. Post exactly like you just saw them and forwarded them to the group.\\n7. Exit silently.\",\n        \"model\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/free\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"-1003606834639\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775817000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775730600005,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 44571,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1775817000006\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"59d38096-1af7-439a-9636-42b25a67b7ae\",\n      \"name\": \"water-reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775727456880,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775809829356,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */2 10-20 * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Kolkata\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"💧 Drink water you idiots. Right now.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\",\n        \"to\": \"-1003606834639\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775817011694,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775809811699,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 17657,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 8,\n        \"lastError\": \"Channel is required when multiple channels are configured: telegram, streamchat Set delivery.channel explicitly or use a main session with a previous channel.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"feee69f8-6016-4f8f-a09c-08b39d9a9191\",\n      \"name\": \"github-backup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774980647416,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775815300402,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 */1 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run these commands: cd /root/.openclaw/workspace && git add -A && git diff --cached --quiet && echo \\\"nothing to commit\\\" || (git commit -m \\\"auto backup\\\" && git push). Report result to Nemesis via message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=7924461837) only if there was an error. If nothing changed, reply NO_REPLY.\",\n        \"model\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/free\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": 